QuestData.Title: Compy Stomp
QuestData.Description: The raptors and saurid of the Zandalari represent a substantial threat to our forces here. They are superb hunting beasts that can track prey over great distances and are often lethal to encounter when caught unawares.$b$bI need you to head into the Beast Pens and cull their numbers. We need to make sure to slay them before they are fully trained.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 5 Raptors and 10 Trained Saurid in the Beast Pens.
